description:
"I-I-I-I... I can't quit you babe..." -- Robert Plant/Led Zeppelin

Good news, Eclipse comics-lovers! I'm back, with enough fills to close out FOURTEEN series!!!! Thanks to the benevolence of Mr Entheogen, who graced my Mega account with 73 comics, I'm overstocked on Eclipse series and I'm passing the savings onto you!

Here's how this is gonna work: I'm gonna upload the entire series in batches of 375-400 Mbs, spread out over four torrents, with each torrent containing 3-4 complete series. The breakdowns:

Part 1

Miracleman Family
New DNAgents
Nightmares
Twisted Tales of Bruce Jones

Part 2

Laser Eraser and Pushbutton
Seduction of the Innocent
The Spider
The Spider - Reign of the Vampire King

Part 3

Strike!
The Masked Man
The Prowler
Zooniverse

Part 4

Cyber 7
Cyber 7 Book II
Scorpio Rose
loose issues

So, let's get started. As always, a big shout-out to the creators and the scanners, AND a special war-whoop for Mr Entheogen! Get 'em, seed 'em!
